"       \"Patient information: Bone problems caused by kidney disease (The Basics)\"",
"      </a>",
"      and",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?8/62/9188?source=see_link\">",
"       \"Patient information: Medicines for chronic kidney disease (The Basics)\"",
"      </a>",
"      )",
"     </li>",
"     <li>",
"      Beyond the Basics topics (see",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?13/5/13398?source=see_link\">",
"       \"Patient information: Chronic kidney disease (Beyond the Basics)\"",
"      </a>",
"      and",
